Class IOFactory

    • commands.IOFactory
  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    Direct Known Subclasses:
    LoadCommand, SaveCommand

    public abstract class IOFactory
extends java.lang.Object
implements Command
    I've used this class in order not to write duplicate code in LoadCommand & SaveCommand. This class has the Level member that will be initiated or saved later on, to implement execute with it's given signature (execute());
